SPD Opposes Issuance of Euro Bonds Soon, Rheinische Post Says

-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 
2011-09-28T22:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/spd-opposes-issuance-of-euro-bonds-soon-rheinische-post-says.html
Carsten Schneider, budget spokesman
for  Germany ’s main opposition  Social Democratic Party , said it
would be “unrealistic” to issue joint euro bonds in the near
term, Rheinische Post Düsseldorf reported, citing Schneider.  The bonds could be issued only if the region’s individual
fiscal policies are harmonized, Schneider said, according to the
newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
